lyrics:
[Verse]
Akela hoon main, tanhaayi ka saathi
Rooth gayi zindagi, kyun na jaane kaunsi baat thi
Dard bhari raatein, dil ko chhoo jaati
Kho gaya hoon khud se, ab kyun na

[Chorus]
Aansuon ki baarish, dil ko behlaati
Kaisi thi woh raat, jisne mujhe rulaati
Akela hoon main, tanhaayi ka saathi
Rooth gayi zindagi, kyun na jaane kaunsi baat thi
